<!-- REPO Setup Guide Modal -->
<div id="repoSetupModal" class="modal-overlay" style="display:none;">
  <div class="modal-content glass" style="max-width:550px;">
    <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:20px;">
      <h3 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;margin:0;">R.E.P.O. Mod Setup</h3>
      <button class="btn-secondary btn-sm" id="closeRepoSetupBtn" style="padding:4px;">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line></svg>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.6;">
      <div class="card-tip" style="background:rgba(52,152,219,0.1);border-left-color:var(--accent);">
        <div class="tip-icon" style="color:var(--accent);">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="tip-title">Requirements</div>
          <div class="tip-desc">The mod requires <b>r2modman</b> or <b>Thunderstore Mod Manager</b>.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--bg3);padding:15px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--border);">
        <div style="font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--dim);">Step 1: Mod Manager</div>
        <p>Download and install <b>r2modman</b> or <b>Thunderstore</b> and select R.E.P.O. as the game.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--bg3);padding:15px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--border);">
        <div style="font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--dim);">Step 2: Open Profiles Folder</div>
        <p>Inside the mod manager, go to <b>Settings &gt; Locations &gt; Browse Data Folder</b>.</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px;">From the opened folder, navigate to <code>REPO/profiles</code>.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--bg3);padding:15px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--border);">
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:8px;">
          <div style="font-weight:700;font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--dim);">Step 3: Install TrinyTok Profile</div>
          <a href="/downloads/trinytokrepo.zip" download class="btn-primary btn-sm" style="text-decoration:none;padding:4px 10px;">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="margin-right:4px;"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"></line></svg>
            Download
          </a>
        </div>
        <p>The file you downloaded is a pre-configured profile with everything needed.</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px;">Extract the ZIP and place the profile folder into the <code>profiles</code> directory. Then select it in the mod manager.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--bg3);padding:15px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--border);">
        <div style="font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--dim);">Step 4: Connect</div>
        <p>Click <b>Start Bridge</b> in this dashboard, then launch R.E.P.O. Once in a game the status will turn <b style="color:var(--success);">GREEN</b>.</p>
      </div>

      <button class="btn-primary" id="repoGotItBtn" style="margin-top:10px;">Got it, let's play!</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
